==評價==

《27件禮服的秘密》獲得許多評價。在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]獲得41%正面影評，154則評論「導演太過遵循了浪漫喜劇的傳統公式，使得27件禮服的秘密過於平凡、看過就忘。」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/27_dresses/ |title=27 Dresses - Movie Reviews, Trailers, Pictures - Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2008-01-18 |publisher=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080117093536/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/27_dresses/ |archivedate=2008-01-17 |deadurl=no }}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]也基於31項評論，在100分中評分為47分<ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/27dresses |title= 27 Dresses (2008): Reviews |accessdate= 2008-01-18 |publisher= [[CBS|CBS]] |work= [[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |archiveurl= https://web.archive.org/web/20080118150335/http://www.metacritic.com/film/titles/27dresses |archivedate= 2008-01-18 |deadurl= no }}</ref>。

